# Cloudflare Pages Redirects Configuration for React SPA
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# Force HTTPS (handled by Cloudflare automatically)
# Redirect www to non-www
https://www.agua-health.com/* https://agua-health.com/:splat 301!

# Redirect old aguahealth-website.pages.dev to custom domain
https://aguahealth-website.pages.dev/* https://agua-health.com/:splat 301!

